INSERT INTO `lei1_article` VALUES ('22', '0', '藁城来了一个美女杀手，很多帅小伙因她而送命！', '<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><hr style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/><blockquote style=\"margin: 0.2em; padding: 10px; max-width: 100%; border: 3px solid rgb(201, 201, 201); color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 13px; text-align: center; box-shadow: rgb(170, 170, 170) 0px 0px 10px; border-image-source: none; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"margin: 0.8em 0px 0.5em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; border: 0px currentcolor; line-height: 25px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0.3em 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; border-radius: 0.5em; border: 0px currentcolor; color: white; display: inline-block; box-shadow: rgb(165, 165, 165) 0.2em 0.2em 0.1em; font-size: 18px; background-color: rgb(147, 98, 98);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; border: 0px currentcolor;\">我是杀手</strong></span></section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; text-align: left; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 112, 192);\">　　在藁城我已经害了很多人，这点我承认，我不该让那些无辜的生命因我而死。可是我要辩解，这不是我的错，是他们每天缠着我，我才下手的。是的，我姓新，名石家庄，很多人都认识我，因为爱我才让他们付出代价。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 1.6em; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p></blockquote><blockquote style=\"margin: 0.2em; padding: 10px; max-width: 100%; border: 3px solid rgb(201, 201, 201); color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 13px; text-align: center; box-shadow: rgb(170, 170, 170) 0px 0px 10px; border-image-source: none; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; text-align: left; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px;\">　　</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 112, 192);\">我的兄弟姐妹很多，可是藁城为什么这么多人喜欢我。我的大叔“黄鹤楼”一般人接近不了，我的大哥“中华”也只是上档次人的专利，我的师弟“将军”，他们又看不上，只有我20元的身价，让藁城更多人接受和喜欢。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 1.6em; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 1.6em; font-size: 14px; text-align: left; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 1.6em; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 112, 192);\">　　我先介绍我自己，我的焦油量是10mg，我身上有3800多种已知的化学物质，他们在享受我的同时，我就开始危害他们的身体。我有一种尼古丁的杀手锏，不但让他们离不开我，还能侵入他们的胃、肺、气管、神经系统，还能用40毫克杀死一个人。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 1.6em; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 1.6em; font-size: 14px; text-align: left; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.6em;\">　　<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 1.6em; color: rgb(0, 112, 192);\">当然我还有一个绝招就是一氧化碳，当吸入较多的我的时候，我便与血红蛋白结合形成大量的碳合血红蛋白，而氧合血红蛋白大大减少，造成组织和器官缺氧，进而使大脑、心脏等多种器官产生损伤。</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 1.6em; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; text-align: left; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px;\">　<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">　</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 112, 192);\">除此之外，我还有烟焦油和苯并芘，这都是我让他们致癌的武器。烟焦油可附着于他们的气管、支气管和肺泡表面产生物理、化学性的刺激，损害人体的呼吸功能。苯并芘就会使他们的肺癌发病率增加5%—15%。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; text-align: left; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">　　如果藁城的一个家庭中有一人喜欢我，那么这一家中的男女老少都要遭殃。喜欢我的家庭，妇女患肺癌明显高于丈夫不吸烟的妇女，同时影响少年儿童的发育，而且易患气管炎和肺炎等疾病。特别是有婴儿的家庭，如果家中有人室内吸烟，烟雾中的尼古丁等有害物质，极易进入大脑，日积月累，就可影响孩子的大脑发育。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 1.6em; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p></blockquote><blockquote style=\"margin: 0.2em; padding: 10px; max-width: 100%; border: 3px solid rgb(201, 201, 201); color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 13px; text-align: center; box-shadow: rgb(170, 170, 170) 0px 0px 10px; border-image-source: none; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"margin: 0.8em 0px 0.5em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; border: 0px currentcolor; line-height: 25px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0.3em 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; border-radius: 0.5em; border: 0px currentcolor; color: white; display: inline-block; box-shadow: rgb(165, 165, 165) 0.2em 0.2em 0.1em; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(147, 98, 98);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; border: 0px currentcolor;\">请远离我</strong></span></section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; text-align: left; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px;\">　　</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0, 112, 192); font-size: 18px;\">在藁城，我是一个不说话，也是最可怕的冷面杀手，各位藁城的老少爷们应该警惕，尽早放弃我，选择健康。如果没有我，你会省钱、体味会比较好、减少得肺癌的几率、减少生白痴小孩的几率、牙齿不会那么黄、看起来也更文雅、食指中指不会很黄、神经系统相对健康，还有就是减少阳痿或性冷淡的机率。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 1.6em; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p></blockquote><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p><p><br/></p>', '小刘', '2015-11-16 08:41:53', '1', '1', '8');
INSERT INTO `lei1_article` VALUES ('23', '0', '天冷了,请大家路上注意', '<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px; line-height: 19.2000007629395px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); line-height: 22px; font-size: 16px;\">今天藁城的气温低达1摄氏度，以后<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">天气一天比一天冷了，寒风凌冽，</span>上学的孩子们衣服穿的厚了，行动也会变得慢了，出行的动作笨拙了。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px; line-height: 19.2000007629395px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250);\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px; line-height: 19.2000007629395px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0, 112, 192); font-size: 16px;\">到了冬天，天黑的早了，气温骤降。而孩子们晚上放学回家，有时还要放学补课，他们迎着夜幕、冒着严寒回家……</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px; text-align: center; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250);\"><br/></p><p><section class=\"135editor\" data-id=\"39\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; white-space: normal; border: 0px none; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250);\"><section style=\"margin: 0.8em 0px 0.5em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; overflow: hidden;\"><section class=\"135brush\" data-brushtype=\"text\" placeholder=\"请输入标题\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; height: 36px; display: inline-block; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-weight: bold; line-height: 36px; float: left; vertical-align: top; background-color: rgb(249, 110, 87);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(227, 108, 9);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12.6315793991089px; line-height: 19.2000007629395px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-size: 16px;\">如果您在路上遇见他们：</span></strong></span></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; display: inline-block; height: 36px; vertical-align: top; border-left-width: 9px; border-left-style: solid; border-left-color: rgb(249, 110, 87); border-top-width: 18px !important; border-top-style: solid !important; border-top-color: transparent !important; border-bottom-width: 18px !important; border-bottom-style: solid !important; border-bottom-color: transparent !important;\"></section></section></section></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px; line-height: 19.2000007629395px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0, 112, 192); font-size: 16px;\">①请开车的司机们</span></strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0, 112, 192); font-size: 16px;\">，不要去责怪孩子们偶尔的抢路，也许是他们太冷了，着急回家。您车里有空调，稍微让他们一下吧。他们还很小，我们每个人都会有小孩，请大家多一份担待，少一分责怪！</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px; line-height: 19.2000007629395px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250);\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px; line-height: 19.2000007629395px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250);\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px; line-height: 19.2000007629395px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0, 112, 192); font-size: 16px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">②路过十字路口时</strong>，司机朋友们请耐心等他们过马路，别跟孩子抢。现在路上人多车多，过十字路口别说是小孩子了，就是大人有时候也会紧张……为爱让路，为孩子们让路。让我们每位司机都行动起来！</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px; line-height: 19.2000007629395px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250);\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px; line-height: 19.2000007629395px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0, 112, 192); font-size: 16px;\">③如果遇到特殊的天气</span></strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0, 112, 192); font-size: 16px;\">，也请开车的各位师傅们看到路边等车的孩子们，请您伸出援手（孩子最好有家长陪同，千万别单独搭乘陌生人的车）能搭顺风车的就让孩子坐上。赠人玫瑰，手有余香。他们会感谢您的！</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px; line-height: 19.2000007629395px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250);\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px; line-height: 19.2000007629395px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250);\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px; line-height: 19.2000007629395px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-size: 16px;\">希望他们可以一如既往的做到这些！<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/>因为有爱，所以温暖！</span></p><p><br/></p>', '小刘', '2015-11-16 08:45:38', '1', '1', '14');
