rgin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\">当的是饭桌党</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\">吃饭不拍照臣妾做不到！朋友圈流行各种党，其中一个群体叫饭桌党。意思就是如果吃饭等上好菜了，不拍到照片，好像感觉没吃到或者没来过一样，菜一上桌，拿出手机，嚓嚓嚓，闪光灯闪到眼前一亮……。遇到这样的人，其他人通常都会想吼一声：“老子快饿死了&quot;！</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p><section class=\"135editor\" data-id=\"1\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; white-space: normal; border: 0px none; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><h2 class=\"135brush\" placeholder=\"请输入标题\" style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 5px 10px; font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; border-left-width: 5px; border-left-style: solid; border-left-color: rgb(216, 40, 33); line-height: 32px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(192, 0, 0);\">凉菜上的快 吃的也快</span></h2><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both;\"></section></section></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\">只要等一道菜超过10分钟，马上就像催命一样！而这个习惯会造成这样：在顾客催上菜之前，菜处于半好的状态，而当顾客以埋单的借口逼迫的时候，菜有可能就会马上变为煮好状态。当然藁城的饭店不一定会这样，多等会吧，好饭还能怕晚？</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; box-sizin